 # 스페인

Holy Isabella, envoy of God, Great Queen of Castille and León, your people celebrate you!


Spain is a beautiful and ancient country, a link between Europe and Africa, one shore on the Mediterranean and the other on the mighty Atlantic Ocean.


The Spanish culture had taken the best of the Christian and Muslim worlds, and was ready to dominate the world for centuries.


